title: #92Noon! Bartley/Chamberlain/Rudy/Leber/Birk!
description: LIVE from the team hotel in Los Angeles, a star-studded 92noon featured Wobby the first hour along with Longmire star/MN native Adam Bartley. 2nd hour offered up former Vikes TE/2x SB winner Byron Chamberlain, then Vikes VP Public affairs Lester Bagley & Pete Bercich...Bercich sticks around as Kyle Rudolph joins, followed by Ben Leber and Matt Birk to close!
